* Independent two-samples t-test
* Import data
import delimited "module_8_data.csv", clear

* 1. Check normality by group
bysort male: swilk salary_normal

* 2. Check homogeneity of variance
sdtest salary_normal, by(male)

* 3. Independent two-samples t-test assuming equal variances
ttest salary_normal, by(male)

* 4. Welch t-test if variances are unequal
ttest salary_normal, by(male) unequal

* One-way ANOVA
* 1. Check normality by rank
bysort rank: swilk salary_normal

* 2. Descriptives and Bartlett's test for equal variances
oneway salary_normal rank, tabulate

* 3. One-way ANOVA
oneway salary_normal rank

* 4. Bonferroni post-hoc comparisons
oneway salary_normal rank, bonferroni
